<div id="optoutform">
    <form action="" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
    <div id="optout-info" class="shadowbox">
        <h2>{L_OPTOUT_TITLE}</h2>
        <div class="sbcontent">
            <table class="notebox notebox-error">
                <tr>
                    <td class="nbox-image"><img src="{V_[scriptpath]}templates/default/images/error.png" width="48" height="48" alt="error" /></td>
                    <td class="nbox-text">{L_OPTOUT_WARNING}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>We only use newsagent to send emails that we feel will be useful to students; we do not use it to
               send out unsolicited emails from outside parties.</p>
            <p>Notifications for individual course units will generally be sent out by academic members staff
               teaching those units via Campus Solutions. As these emails contain important information related
               to course units then you cannot opt out of receiving them.</p>
            <p>We may use newsagent to distribute information that we feel you may be interested in receiving. In
               this case, due to GDPR requirements, we offer you the opportunity to unsubscribe to all non-essential
               news feeds. </p>
            <p>Even if you opt out of emails from Newsagent, you may still receive email notifications for
               articles published in the following feeds. These are important feeds that communicate information
               relevant to your education, safety, or mental health.</p>
            <ul>
            ***overrides***
            </ul>
            <div class="textwrapper optoutline">
                 <dl class="input">
                     <dd><label for="opt-opt" class="check"><input type="checkbox" name="optout" id="opt-opt" ***optout*** />{L_OPTOUT_OPTOUT}</label></dd>
                 </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="submitbox">
                <input type="submit" class="button blue" name="setoptout" id="setoptout" value="{L_OPTOUT_SUBMIT}" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </form>
</div>
